{"tid":599061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Line today係咪已經俾五毛佔領埋？","createTime":"2018-03-20T05:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T07:50:12.000Z","uid":1065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"98091395e092759793a8f36fb8dd73fe6d03d6c2","tid":599061,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:46:26.000Z","msg":"有玩開line嘅話可能都會留意到最近成日都有個line today嘅pop up<br />\n咁佢就會每日揀啲新聞出嚟send俾你睇<br />\n<br />\n咁今日就見到個新聞講美國有自動駕駛嘅uber撞死人 出事嗰陣冇減到速<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/YE7ZQa?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2FYE7ZQa%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=Z%2Bo1ZBmCoAcqYYG%2BOstpWr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=6c94e38c\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/YE7ZQa?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n咁拉落去就見到有人講 其實架uber係用緊支那製嘅自動煞車系統<br />\n但篇新聞就隻字不提個系統係邊度整嘅<br />\n<br />\n之後然後條友就開始俾人咬 同埋成堆人出嚟幫支那系統護航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/134216_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F134216_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=349cede3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又屈鳩佢政治化<br />\n明明人哋只係指出系統係支那整嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/134225_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F134225_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=efeed132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又係呢種叫人走嘅論調<br />\n明明連人哋係咪喺香港住緊都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/134238_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F134238_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9d041777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底香港仲有冇一個新聞網嘅comment section係未比五毛污染？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e39cf80f1eadaae60bd8b682192422b14e51b2","tid":599061,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:47:18.000Z","msg":"事實係香港好多廢中都係呢種思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09e372de07516f15f98c871de234196ae403f78","tid":599061,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:48:53.000Z","msg":"因為正常人集中哂係連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bcd5dce18ecbd526c79adc351b894d8df0296a","tid":599061,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:49:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8ab4911cd04e94138fdcf9d4a1b2aa0be449dd2","tid":599061,"uid":6111,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:52:56.000Z","msg":"我發現有個好奇怪既現象 <br />\n好多4-60歲既廢中唔知點解好撐支共<br />\n反而60歲以上果班就好多都反既<br />\n唔知係咪佢地以前比人逼害搞到落左黎香港<br />\n之後生左40-60歲果班人<br />\n但果班人就on99咁收少少甜頭就以為支共好所以咁盲撐"},{"pid":"b4efdd6610ad64de944e89c7159088141271a775","tid":599061,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8ab4911cd04e94138fdcf9d4a1b2aa0be449dd2","tid":599061,"uid":6111,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:52:56.000Z","msg":"我發現有個好奇怪既現象 <br />\n好多4-60歲既廢中唔知點解好撐支共<br />\n反而60歲以上果班就好多都反既<br />\n唔知係咪佢地以前比人逼害搞到落左黎香港<br />\n之後生左40-60歲果班人<br />\n但果班人就on99咁收少少甜頭就以為支共好所以咁盲撐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T06:11:56.000Z","msg":"7,80歲以上個班老野好多都係內戰打輸左 又反共先走佬黎香港 <br />\n相反班廢中經歷完67暴動仲會奶共 真係痴鳩線"},{"pid":"e59446b117cf309f9773351ff93eebffd0877d36","tid":599061,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4efdd6610ad